You are hereby directed to preserve, and not to alter, delete, overwrite, or destroy, any of the following:

- All correspondence (email, letter, SMS, chat, voicemail, call logs) between your organization and me, or internally referencing me or this matter.
- All claim files, case notes, adjuster notes, supervisor reviews, vendor reports, appraisals, and internal memoranda.
- All policy documents, contract documents, form sets, and endorsements in effect on or near the loss date.
- All audio/video recordings and any metadata associated with them.
- Any backup tapes or archives that might otherwise be recycled in the ordinary course of business.

This preservation obligation continues until the matter is fully resolved or until we mutually agree in writing that it has ended. Routine document-retention schedules must be suspended as to this matter.

